Package: autoMR
Type: Package
Title: Automated Mendelian Randomization Workflows and Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(
      person("Kelin", "Zhong", email = "kelin.zhong@uconn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Chia-Ling", "Kuo", email = "kuo@uchc.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides a streamlined workflow for summarizing, analyzing, and visualizing
    the results of Mendelian Randomization (MR) studies. Includes tools for generating
    SNP-level and method-level forest plots and scatter plots, and for running multiple MR
    estimators (including IVW, RAPS, Egger, MR-PRESSO, GRIP, and MR-Horse) in a unified format.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2)
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 4.0.1),
    dplyr (>= 1.1.4),
    tidyr (>= 1.3.1),
    MendelianRandomization (>= 0.10.0),
    R2jags (>= 0.8-9),
    coda (>= 0.19-4.1),
    nortest (>= 1.0-4),
    grDevices,
    graphics,
    stats,
    utils
URL: https://github.com/KelinZhong/autoMR
BugReports: https://github.com/KelinZhong/autoMR/issues
